work_description: Complete Interior Remodel and Partial Demo to replace windows per plan. Remodel to include existing habitable attic, new attic stair to replace existing, new half bath, remodel of 2 existing bathrooms including finishes and fixture replacements, new water heater, refinish floors, new wall paneling in living room, replace hearth at fireplace, replace window sashes. Existing non-complying deck over rear lot line, not affected by work in this permit. **REVISION #01 10/13/14: Relocate stair from middle hall to Den. Remove floor joists in this area. Demolish existing stair and rail and replace floor joists. Widen attic hall to 3'-8" by moving south wall. Two new closets open to hall. Powder bath in olde stair location (instead of Den as in Plan #1). Building new walls for closet in old Den location, facing Master Bedroom. Expand length of attic Bath 2 to 8'-4" and relocate sink adjacent to toilet.**
Remove tub and surround. Install new solid surface shower pan and valve. Install new solid surface surround.
